OL,3,COxfordshire man fears financial hit
OL,4,Cfrom rising heating oil prices
OL,6,FAn Oxfordshire man has expressed
OL,7,Fconcern about the impacts the war in
OL,8,FIran is having on rising heating oil
OL,9,Fprices back home.
OL,11,FTony Parker, 80, from Towersey, said
OL,12,Fhe is now paying around 130p per litre
OL,13,Fof kerosene - an amount which is more
OL,14,Fthan double what it costed him before
OL,15,Fthe conflict started.
OL,17,FMr Parker, who is due to retire later
OL,18,Fthis year, told ITV Meridian he fears
OL,19,Fthe financial hit he and his wife will
OL,20,Fbe faced with, once he has left his
OL,21,Fjob as a surveyor.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
