FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774368667
OL,3,COxfordshire man fears financial hit
OL,4,Cfrom rising heating oil prices
OL,6,FHe said: "Well, at the moment, as I am
OL,7,Fstill working, it's ok. We can manage
OL,8,Fit. But when I retire in a couple of
OL,9,Fmonths time it's going to make a big
OL,10,Fdifference because that would be
OL,11,Fprobably 18 per cent of our pension."
OL,13,FKerosene, the fuel used for heating
OL,14,Foil, has been especially affected by
OL,15,Fthe Middle East conflict, with prices
OL,16,Fsoaring faster than petrol or gas.
OL,18,F'When I retire in a couple of months
OL,19,Ftime it's going to make a big
OL,20,Fdifference'
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
