FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774368667
OL,3,COxfordshire man fears financial hit
OL,4,Cfrom rising heating oil prices
OL,6,FThe government has pledged #50 million
OL,7,Fto help support low-income families
OL,8,Fwith the rising cost of heating oil.
OL,10,FHowever, Mr Parker said he and his
OL,11,Fwife are ineligible to benefit as they
OL,12,Fdo not qualify as a low-income
OL,13,Fhousehold.
OL,15,F"We're in that middle bit where we
OL,16,Fdon't get hit," he said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
