OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774368667
OL,3,COxfordshire man fears financial hit
OL,4,Cfrom rising heating oil prices
OL,6,F"We've got no money. We don't get the
OL,7,Fadvantages of whether you've got no
OL,8,Fmoney or whether you've got a lot of
OL,9,Fmoney, it doesn't matter anyway, so
OL,10,Fwe're in that position."
OL,12,FIn Great Britain, the price of heating
OL,13,Foil is not regulated in the same way
OL,14,Fas gas and electricity, which can lead
OL,15,Fto market volatility and exploit
OL,16,Fconsumers.
OL,18,FMr Parker said he would like the
OL,19,Fgovernment, in an effort to address
OL,20,Fthis, introduce a heating oil price
OL,21,Fcap.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774368667
OL,3,COxfordshire man fears financial hit
OL,4,Cfrom rising heating oil prices
OL,6,FHe added that he is hopeful the price
OL,7,Fof heating oil will eventually start
OL,8,Fto fall, but is concerned when exactly
OL,9,Fthat might happen.
OL,11,FA government spokesperson said: "We
OL,12,Fknow that people are concerned about
OL,13,Fthe potential impact of global
OL,14,Fconflicts on the cost of living.
OL,16,F"While it is too soon to know the full
OL,17,Fimpact of this crisis, as the
OL,18,Fchancellor said, she will take the
OL,19,Fnecessary decisions to help families
OL,20,Fwith the cost of living and protect
OL,21,Fthe public finances.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
