PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774368667
OL,3,COxfordshire man fears financial hit
OL,4,Cfrom rising heating oil prices
OL,6,F"We have extended the 5p fuel duty
OL,7,Fcut, expanded the Warm Homes Discount
OL,8,Fto take #150 a year off of energy
OL,9,Fbills for six million households, and
OL,10,Fthe energy price cap will protect
OL,11,Fhouseholds for the next three months
OL,12,Fas bills will fall by #117."
